import React from 'react'
import { BrowserRouter, Route } from 'react-router-dom'
import Ejercicio from './pages/Ejercicios'


function App(){
    <BrowserRouter>
        <Route path="/exercise" component={Ejercicio}/>
        <Route path="/exercise" component={EjercicioNuevo}/>
    </BrowserRouter>
}


export default App
